{"tid":582141,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Ps4 pro club D1 垃圾隊誠招多功能隊員","createTime":"2018-03-06T02:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T03:49:31.000Z","uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"859ba9c10917b87b85865a3fcc0678bd8610a331","tid":582141,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>麻煩睇完岩FEEL先TG<br />\n唔好哂大家時間<br />\nADD 完又唔入黎玩</strong><br />\n<br />\nCM X 1 (可PT 踢閘)<br />\nLB RB X 20<br />\nGK X 1<br />\n<br />\n踢控傳 傳波準 決定快<br />\n實力中下但氣氛良好<br />\n<ins>唔好介意隊波多人</ins><br />\n最好咩位都識打下<br />\n球王性格就不了<br />\n希望大家尊重大家，同時亦都可以互相比意見<br />\n只收固定球員 會周圍走周圍打就唔需要 要開咪<br />\n歡迎新手中手老手勁人入隊大家交流學野<br />\n新手都唔好介意希望大家踢下開心下<br />\n亦會參加唔同比賽，希望大家一齊進步<br />\n一星期至少可以出席三天<br />\n開波時間：通常夜晚10點後玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntelegram : wengerhoball<br />\n<br />\nadd完麻煩CHING pm自己位置"},{"pid":"7149c0a88a82f28c463737e5ee7a98b036eb98d0","tid":582141,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c5cffdb1cb0cb15141a1b2659b8cabd2f5bab5","tid":582141,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7149c0a88a82f28c463737e5ee7a98b036eb98d0","tid":582141,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b52685863242a98c649827cf4e29e0a0aca016f","tid":582141,"uid":126952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:38:22.000Z","msg":"打pro club對過你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ecd3fa7e5a72954b83c3784ef34e2b7f3810eb","tid":582141,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b52685863242a98c649827cf4e29e0a0aca016f","tid":582141,"uid":126952,"l